<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>DeFi on Eric SJ Research</title><link>https://ericsjresearch.com/zh-cn/tags/defi/</link><description>Recent content in DeFi on Eric SJ Research</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ericsjresearch.com/zh-cn/tags/defi/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Hyperliquid商业模式分析：一个链上交易所如何捕获现金流</title><link>https://ericsjresearch.com/zh-cn/web3/hyperliquid%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%93%BE%E4%B8%8A%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%89%80%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%8D%95%E8%8E%B7%E7%8E%B0%E9%87%91%E6%B5%81/</link><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://ericsjresearch.com/zh-cn/web3/hyperliquid%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E9%93%BE%E4%B8%8A%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%89%80%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E6%8D%95%E8%8E%B7%E7%8E%B0%E9%87%91%E6%B5%81/</guid><description>Hyperliquid 的核心不是简单复制中心化交易所，而是在链上订单簿、永续合约流动性和协议收入之间建立现金流闭环。</description></item><item><title>Web3已经验证的五种商业模式</title><link>https://ericsjresearch.com/zh-cn/web3/web3%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%94%E7%A7%8D%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/</link><pubDate>Tue, 07 Jul 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://ericsjresearch.com/zh-cn/web3/web3%E5%B7%B2%E7%BB%8F%E9%AA%8C%E8%AF%81%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%94%E7%A7%8D%E5%95%86%E4%B8%9A%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F/</guid><description>Web3 并非所有叙事都能变成商业模式，目前更清晰的收入模型主要集中在交易、稳定币、基础设施、金融协议和网络型应用。</description></item></channel></rss>